:: MODEL-VIEW-CONTROLLER  ::

path --> route --> controller --> view  --
 ^                    |             ^    |
 |                    |             |    |
 |                    ----> model ---    |
 -----------------------------------------


path: http module
route: routes module (....)
contoller: posts module etc.
model: post class etc
view: template

:: ERRORS/EXCEPTIONS ::

Exceptions: For developers
Fatal errors: For user
